---
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-head-left">
        <div class="section-label">01 — About</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          A middle schooler between <span class="italic-serif">pixels &amp; code</span>.
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <article class="glass card card--about">
        <p class="lede">
          Hi, I'm <strong>Tae Young Ryu</strong> — a <strong>middle school student</strong> in Seoul.
          On Entry and Figma I go by <span class="highlight">@ty2035</span>.
        </p>
        <p>
          I started making tiny games on Entry when I was younger and got hooked on the feeling
          that something on a screen could move just because I told it to.
          These days I design in Figma and bring the result to life in code —
          learning a little more every week.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe the best interfaces are the ones that <em>disappear</em>.
          Accuracy over flair. Rhythm over information. Feel over features.
        </p>
      </article>

      <aside class="about-side">
        <div class="glass card card--stat">
          <div class="stat-label">Stage</div>
          <div class="stat-value stat-value--sm">
            <span class="pulse-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Middle school student
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass card card--stat">
          <div class="stat-label">Based in</div>
          <div class="stat-value">Seoul, <span class="italic-serif">Korea</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass card card--stat">
          <div class="stat-label">Working with</div>
          <div class="stat-tags">
            <span class="tag">Entry</span>
            <span class="tag">Figma</span>
            <span class="tag">HTML</span>
            <span class="tag">CSS</span>
            <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
